en_4199019_0	The bond for UPFA Presidential Candidate, President Mahinda Rajapaksa, was deposited on Monday.
en_4199019_1	The bond was deposited on behalf of President Mahinda Rajapaksa, by UPFA General Secretary Minister Susil Premajayantha, at the Elections Secretariat.
en_4199019_2	SLFP National Organiser Minister Basil Rajapaksa, General Secretary Minister Anura Priyadarshana Yapa and Leader of the Mahajana Eksath Peramuna, Minister Dinesh Gunawardena, were also present at the occasion.
en_4199019_3	Minister Susil Premajayantha commenting on the preparations ahead of the presidential poll noted that they have already begun to establish steering committees for polling booths, electorates as well as districts.
en_4199019_4	Minister Dinesh Gunawardene commented that 14 political parties have joined hands with the SLFP to secure the victory of President Mahinda Rajapaksa.
en_4199019_5	Minister Anura Yapa echoed the same views and stated that all constituent parties of the UPFA would work together for this purpose.
